<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Irreligious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Irreligious,</orth> impious, ungodly: <cit><quote>a thousand i. cursed hours,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.242" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 242</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O cruel i. piety,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 1.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 130</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an i. Moor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.121" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 121</bibl></cit>.
